    <p>1. Company is in business of cataloging, transporting, and storing Items (as defined below), as more fully described in <b>Section 3</b> below (the &ldquo;<b>Services</b>&rdquo;); and</p>
    <p>2. Customer wishes to engage Company to provide the Services with respect to garments and other articles of clothing, shoes and accessories (the &ldquo;<b>Items</b>&rdquo;) provided by Customer as may be amended from time to time in accordance with the terms and conditions set forth below.</p>
    <p>NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration of the mutual covenants set forth herein and other good valuable consideration, the receipt and sufficiency of which are hereby acknowledged, the parties do hereby agree as follows:</p>
    <p>3. <b>Description of Services</b>. Company agrees to provide the following services to Customer or on Customer&rsquo;s behalf:</p>
