    <p>(5) Customer shall pay an Appointment fee of forty dollars ($40.00) to the Company for each Appointment; including both Item pickup and drop-off. Please note however that depending on which membership option is selected by the Customer, Customer may be entitled to one complimentary Appointment per month.</p>
